<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Na kumsawt mun ding khawi taka?
 Ziehi nang leh kei dawt I hi;
 Ei hilh in bangti'n na dawng die?
 Na kumsawt mun ding khawitak a?

[V2]
 Kumsawt mun ding! kumsawt mun ding!
 Na kumsawt mun ding khawitak a?

[V3]
 2. Tun tampi'n Krista a tel ui,
 A gitlohnau nungheisan in;
 A van gam nuom chuh chang dingin,
 Na kumsawt mun ding khawitak a?

[V4]
 3. Lampi zang leh chip taihsan in,
 Lamphei nuomah na chieh zel chun;
 A tawpna bang a hung hi dem?
 Na kumsawt mun ding khawitak a?

[V5]
 4. Kihei in, tun hun ging ziengin,
 Hehpih, Hukdampa hat gingin;
 Na dawnna lawpum zie hina,
 Hukdama ka hitai kumsawtin!
 Kum khawsawt in! Kum khawsawt in!
 Hukdam ka hitai, kumsawt in!</lyrics>
<title>WHERE WILL YOU SPEND ETERNITY?</title>
<hymn_number>157</hymn_number>
</song>